title: The Horoscope Said No, My Heart (D*ck) Said Yes
description:
Lauren and Jeremy dive into the world of love languages. Lauren checks their relationship's compatibility through personality types, and Jeremy expresses his general disinterest in horoscopes. Lauren is shocked to hear Jeremy's secret dating app technique.
